&lt;li&gt;Strategic Negotiations: Partner with CS, Marketing, and Legal teams to prepare for and execute complex contract negotiations and renewals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Forecasting &amp;amp; Reporting: Maintain an accurate pipeline and forecast with clear next steps; track all activities in Salesforce, Gong, Outreach, and Catalyst&lt;/li&gt;
