&lt;li&gt;3+ years of proven experience handling and negotiating renewals, upsells, and cross-sells in a high-performance SaaS environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to build strategic relationships at various levels, both internally and externally&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Salesforce, Gong.io, Outreach, and Catalyst (or similar CRM/CS tools)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be highly organized, process-oriented, and capable of working to strict targets and deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
